'''Hamza Mohamed Abdelkarim E Selim''' ({{langx|ar|حمزة محمد عبد الكريم سليم}}; born 1 January 2008) is an Egyptian professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Striker (association football)|striker]] for {{Spanish football updater|Barcelona Atlètic}} club [[FC Barcelona Atlètic|Barcelona Atlètic]], on loan from [[Egyptian Premier League]] club [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]], and the [[Egypt national football team|Egypt national team]].

==Club career==
He used to represent FC Kuala Lumpur during his time in Malaysia after he started from Little League Soccer, when he was 8 years old which won he the first ever KL Cup in 2016.<ref>{{Cite AV media |url=https://www.facebook.com/reel/938895291565971/ |title=1.1K views {{!}} Maxim Events on Reels |language=en |access-date=2026-05-22 |via=www.facebook.com}}</ref>

Abdelkarim joined the academy of [[Al Ahly SC|Al Ahly]] in 2020, after passing trials with the club. He was called up to the Al Ahly senior squad for the first time in January 2025, ahead of an [[Egyptian Premier League]] match against [[Pharco FC|Pharco]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.egypttelegraph.com/article/112526/%D8%A8%D8%B9%D8%AF-%D8%B8%D9%87%D9%88%D8%B1%D9%87-%D9%84%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%88%D9%84%D9%89-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D9%87%D9%84%D9%8A|title=بعد ظهوره للمرة الأولى في قائمة الأهلي.. من هو حمزة عبدالكريم؟|trans-title=After his first appearance on Al-Ahly's roster... Who is Hamza Abdelkarim|date=21 January 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=egypttelegraph.com|language=ar}}</ref> Despite not making his debut in the game, the decision to call him up at such a young age drew praise from Egypt national youth team coach Tamer Hassan, who tipped Abdelkarim to become a key player for Al Ahly.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://elcaptain.dostor.org/216657|title=مدرب منتخب الشباب يشيد بقرار انضمام حمزة عبدالكريم لقائمة الأهلى أمام فاركو|trans-title=The youth team coach praises the decision to include Hamza Abdelkarim in Al-Ahly's squad against Pharco|date=21 January 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=elcaptain.dostor.org|language=ar}}</ref>

The following month, on 6 February 2025, Abdelkarim would make his professional debut for the club, coming on as a late substitute for [[Emam Ashour]] in a 2–1 win against [[Petrojet SC|Petrojet]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.egypttelegraph.com/article/117461/%D8%AF%D8%AE%D9%84-%D8%A8%D8%AF%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8B%D8%A7-%D9%84%D8%A5%D9%85%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%B9%D8%A7%D8%B4%D9%88%D8%B1-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%87%D9%88-%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%B2%D8%A9|title=دخل بديلًا لإمام عاشور.. من هو حمزة عبد الكريم ناشئ الأهلي الجديد؟|trans-title=He replaced Emam Ashour.. Who is Hamza Abdelkarim, Al-Ahly's new junior|date=6 February 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=egypttelegraph.com|language=ar}}</ref> In doing so, he became the youngest player to represent the club in the 21st century, surpassing [[Ramadan Sobhi]]'s record by nine days.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.almasryalyoum.com/news/details/3371647|title=حمزة عبدالكريم أصغر لاعب يشارك مع الأهلي|trans-title=Hamza Abdelkarim is the youngest player to play for Al-Ahly|date=6 February 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=almasryalyoum.com|language=ar}}</ref> The following week, it was reported that Dutch [[Eredivisie]] club [[Feyenoord]] were interested in taking Abdelkarim on trial.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sport.elfagr.org/5119168|title=فاينورد الهولندي يطلب ضم حمزة عبدالكريم.. والأهلي يدرس القرار|trans-title=Dutch club Feyenoord requests to sign Hamza Abdelkarim, and Al-Ahly is studying the decision|date=10 February 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=sport.elfagr.org|language=ar}}</ref> In January 2026, he extended his contract with Al Ahly until 2028.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.ysscores.com/en/news/13901093/Hamza-Abdel-Karim-Extends-Contract-with-Al-Ahly-Before-Moving-to-Barcelona |title=Hamza Abdel Karim Extends Contract with Al Ahly Before Moving to Barcelona |publisher=ysscores.com |date=30 January 2026 }}</ref>

On 1 February 2026, Abdelkarim joined [[Segunda Federación]] side [[FC Barcelona Atlètic]] on loan until the end of the 2025–26 season, with an option to buy.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.fcbarcelona.com/en/football/barca-b/news/4442438/hamza-abdelkarim-joins-barca-atletic |title=Hamza Abdelkarim joins Barça Atlètic |publisher=FC Barcelona |date=1 February 2026 }}</ref> He made his debut for [[FC Barcelona (youth)|Barcelona Juvenil]] on 8 March, scoring a goal in a 2–2 draw with the youth team of [[SD Huesca]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.panafricafootball.com/article/video-hamza-abdelkarim-scores-first-barcelona-youth-goal-on-debut-against-huesca |title=Video: Hamza AbdelKarim scores first Barcelona youth goal on debut against Huesca |publisher=Pan-Africa Football |date=8 March 2026 }}</ref>

==International career==
Abdelkarim represented Egypt at the 2024 UNAF U-17 Tournaments held in [[2024 UNAF U-17 Tournament|Algeria]] and [[2024 UNAF U-17 Tournament (Morocco)|Morocco]], scoring three goals in both to help his nation to both titles.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://trend.elwatanplus.com/%d8%ad%d9%85%d8%b2%d9%87-%d8%b9%d8%a8%d8%af%d8%a7%d9%84%d9%83%d8%b1%d9%8a%d9%85/|title=حمزه عبدالكريم يصعد ضمن صفوف نادي الأهلي بعد تلاقيه رجال المباراة مرتين متتاليتين في منتخب مصر للناشئين|trans-title=Hamza Abdelkarim is promoted to the Al Ahly squad after facing the men of the match twice in a row in the Egyptian youth national team|date=13 February 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=trend.elwatanplus.com|language=ar}}</ref> He was called up again for the [[2025 U-17 Africa Cup of Nations]], but was unable to help Egypt progress beyond the group stage, despite scoring twice. His Man-of-the-Match performance against [[Angola national under-17 football team|Angola]], including scoring once in Egypt's 2–1 victory, earned his nation a place at the [[2025 FIFA U-17 World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sport.elwatannews.com/ar/1/1/1227065/%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%B2%D8%A9-%D8%B9%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%83%D8%B1%D9%8A%D9%85-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%B5%D8%AF-%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%A6%D8%B2%D8%A9-%D8%A3%D9%81%D8%B6%D9%84-%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%A8-%D9%81%D9%8A-%D9%85%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%A9-%D9%85%D8%B5%D8%B1-%D9%88%D8%A3%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%88%D9%84%D8%A7|title=حمزة عبدالكريم يحصد جائزة أفضل لاعب في مباراة مصر وأنجولا|trans-title=Hamza Abdelkarim wins the best player award in the Egypt-Angola match|date=12 April 2025|access-date=19 May 2025|website=sport.elwatannews.com|language=ar}}</ref>

On 20 May 2026, Abdelkarim was named in [[Egypt national football team|Egypt]]'s squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.efa.com.eg/ar/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A3%D8%AE%D8%A8%D8%A7%D8%B1/%D8%AD%D8%B3%D8%A7%D9%85-%D8%AD%D8%B3%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%86-%D9%82%D8%A7%D8%A6%D9%85%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D9%86%D8%AA%D8%AE%D8%A8-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%88%D8%B7%D9%86%D9%8A-%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A8%D8%AF%D8%A6%D9%8A%D8%A9-%D8%A7%D8%B3%D8%AA%D8%B9%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%AF%D8%A7-%D9%84%D9%83%D8%A3%D8%B3-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%85/|title=حسام حسن يعلن قائمة المنتخب الوطني المبدئية استعداداً لكأس العالم|trans-title=Hossam Hassan announces the preliminary squad for the national team in preparation for the World Cup|publisher=[[Egyptian Football Association]] |date=May 20, 2026 |access-date=May 20, 2026 |language=en}}</ref> He made his debut on 28 May, as an 86th-minute substitute in a 1–0 [[Exhibition game|friendly]] win against [[Russia national football team|Russia]].<ref>https://www.fifa.com/en/match-centre/match/cesdwwnxbc5fmajgroc0hqzy2/dezv8l0fzgcxtejl0dwmy1gyc/2m1wojm5bt709wu4kugtytxqs/eroqzn1trwb812wczpi3ys844</ref>

